{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2396","labels_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2396/labels{/name}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2396/comments","events_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/issues/2396/events","html_url":"https://github.com/owncloud/core/issues/2396","id":12110659,"number":2396,"title":"[5.0] sessions can't start when php is set to use memcache as the backend","user":{"login":"interfasys","id":323220,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/164eb04275907e34b5a3773c66a210d2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd71bba295ff7dccd28ff4e760ce95d70.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"164eb04275907e34b5a3773c66a210d2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys","html_url":"https://github.com/interfasys","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false},"labels":[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/owncloud/core/labels/bug","name":"bug","color":"fc2929"}],"state":"closed","assignee":null,"milestone":null,"comments":8,"created_at":"2013-03-17t16:19:38z","updated_at":"2013-03-19t11:05:59z","closed_at":"2013-03-19t11:05:59z","pull_request":{"html_url":null,"diff_url":null,"patch_url":null},"body":"owncloud 5.0 is giving us error 500s because sessions can't start.\r\nafter investigation, we've found that it's because owncloud is overriding our php.ini's session.save_path which is set to the memcache server.\r\n\r\nit seems the problem comes from line 1 in lib/base.php\r\n<?php @ini_set('upload_tmp_dir',dirname($_server['request_filename']).'/tmp'); @ini_set('session.save_path',dirname($_server['request_filename']).'/tmp');?>\r\n\r\n\r\n### expected behaviour\r\nsessions should start and people should be able to use owncloud\r\n\r\n### actual behaviour\r\nthe server returns error 500\r\n\r\n### steps to reproduce\r\n1. go to the install url\r\n2. stare at your pretty customized error 500 page ;)\r\n\r\n### server configuration\r\noperating system: freebsd 8\r\n\r\nweb server: apache\r\n\r\ndatabase: maradb\r\n\r\nphp version: 5.4.11\r\n\r\nowncloud version: 5.0\r\n\r\n#### owncloud log (data/owncloud.log)\r\n{\"app\":\"php\",\"message\":\"session_start(): failed to initialize storage module: memcache (path: \\/tmp) at \\/lib\\/base.php#328\",\"level\":4,\"time\":1363536877}","closed_by":{"login":"interfasys","id":323220,"avatar_url":"https://gravatar.com/avatar/164eb04275907e34b5a3773c66a210d2?d=https%3a%2f%2fidenticons.github.com%2fd71bba295ff7dccd28ff4e760ce95d70.png&r=x","gravatar_id":"164eb04275907e34b5a3773c66a210d2","url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys","html_url":"https://github.com/interfasys","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/interfasys/received_events","type":"user","site_admin":false}}